title: Clinical Metaproteomics 2: Discovery
questions: How to extract microbial and Human protein and peptide sequences from the results
objectives: Perform Database searching using two algorithms
Generate a microbial peptide panel for verification
key_points: Employ SearchGUI/PeptideShaker and MaxQuant for database searching
Extraction of confident microbial peptides for verification

workflows.title: WF2_Discovery-Workflow
